OL,3,CWho are Jersey's political parties for
OL,4,Cthe 2026 election?
OL,6,FThere will be two political parties
OL,7,Fand one political movement represented
OL,8,Fat Jersey's 2026 election in June.
OL,10,FThis compares to four political
OL,11,Fparties and one movement in the 2022
OL,12,Felection.
OL,14,FReform Jersey was the most successful
OL,15,Fparty in 2022 winning 10 seats, whilst
OL,16,FJersey Alliance won a sizable share of
OL,17,Fthe popular vote, it only won a single
OL,18,Fseat, almost all of its members in the
OL,19,FAssembly were voted out.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
