OL,3,CWho are Jersey's political parties for
OL,4,Cthe 2026 election?
OL,6,FIn 2022 Jersey Liberal Conservatives
OL,7,Fand Progress Party received 2 and 1
OL,8,Fseats respectively. Parties have not
OL,9,Fproved popular in Jersey's elections
OL,10,Fin the past with two thirds of those
OL,11,Felected in 2022 standing as
OL,12,Findependents.
OL,14,FThis time only two political parties
OL,15,Fhave registered they are Reform Jersey
OL,16,Fand People First, but there's also a
OL,17,Fpolitical movement called Value Jersey.
OL,19,FValue Jersey has produced a manifesto,
OL,20,Fwhich candidates can endorse, but its
OL,21,Fname won't appear on ballot paper.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
